(17, 6, '<NMFFDAece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae006E3486hdfcbank_mid_prod15@mailers.hdfcbank.net>', 'information@mailers.hdfcbank.net', '=?UTF-8?Q?=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F_6_Rising_Frauds_everyone_should_know?=', ' Unlock your safety guide   \r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTo view this message in HTML format, click here:\r\n https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684ea&e=cDE9JTQwRzdOd0lheDYxVTdJdUhTUWJ1Tlo2aG1DSDRsb3ZvZk5DNVlTQlMlMkZpOVdZVVFVd01lbENNVmNZbDY4eThTRGRjb25NMUFmMFpYMWJadHZNSVhPWEw3ZyUzRCUzRA&s=47rWgNQdFd74c1oUNyU4cSTXeVYIy1WfIjOxWhkDKBI \r\nor paste this link in a Web browser\r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------	\r\nDear Customer, 	\r\nGreetings from HDFC Bank! \r\nWe understand the importance of feeling safe while banking. Fraudsters are finding new ways to trick customers, but a little awareness can help you stop them and keep your banking experience safe & worry-free. 	\r\nFrauds You Should Know About And How to Stay Protected: 	\r\n	\r\n\r\nType of Fraud 	What Happens 	How to Stay Safe 	\r\n1. APK Fraud 	Fraudsters send fake app links  via SMS or WhatsApp. Once installed, they can access your phone and misuse your personal data. 	Do:  Download apps only from the Play Store or App Store. \r\nDont:  Click on unknown links  or files sent by unknown sources. 	\r\n2. Investment Fraud 	Fraudsters promise very high profits through fake trading or investment websites. 	Do:  Invest only through SEBI-registered platforms. \r\nDont:  Believe offers that sound too good to be true. 	\r\n3. Digital Arrest Fraud 	Fraudsters impersonate police or government officials  and threaten false legal action  to collect money. \r\nThere is no such thing as a digital arrest  under Indian law. 	Do: Stay calm  and hang up immediately. \r\nDont:  Share personal details or transfer money  to unknown callers. 	\r\n4. Job Offer Fraud 	Fraudsters offer fake job opportunities  and ask for fees or banking details. 	Do: Verify  the companys authenticity before applying. \r\nDont:  Pay for job offers  or share your Bank Account details. 	\r\n5. Parcel Delivery Fraud 	Fraudsters claim your parcel contains illegal items  and demand payment  to avoid fake legal action. 	Do:  Contact the courier company directly  using official contact details. \r\nDont: Panic  or make any payment  without confirming with the courier company. 	\r\n6. Romance Fraud 	Fraudsters build fake online relationships to gain trust and later ask for money or personal details. 	Do:  Verify identities, check photos/details, and inform family. \r\nDont:  Send money or share personal or banking information with someone you havent met. 	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684f5&e=dXRtX21lZGl1bT1FbWFpbCZjbXBuX29yaWdpbj1hY2N2OCZhY2NpZD1oZGJrMTgzMjM4JmFjYmlkPWVjZTA5Y2RmLTEyOWItNDk2Yy1hYmM4LTg2YzUwNTEzM2RhZQ&s=Mj-QKxPdz5wBsEryrA6HONInpGXBA9DifLSUK2zpY9M Know more about frauds 	\r\n	\r\nStay Secure with These Simple Banking Habits 	\r\n	\r\n\r\n1. 	Use HDFC Banks official website or MobileBanking app for all your banking needs. 	\r\n	\r\n2. 	Calls starting with the 1600 prefix are official service or transaction calls. You can safely answer them. 	\r\n	\r\n3. 	Keep your contact details updated so you receive alerts on your transactions. 	\r\n	\r\n4. 	Be cautious of unknown calls or messages that offer rewards, refunds, jobs, or KYC updates. 	\r\n	\r\n5. 	Avoid downloading unknown apps or clicking unverified links. 	\r\n	\r\n6. 	Review app permissions regularly and remove unnecessary SMS or call access to keep your data safe. 	\r\n	\r\n7. 	Report suspicious messages on the Chakshu Portal at  https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684f6 https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684f7 	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\nIf You Ever Face Fraud - Remember the LBW Rule 	\r\n	\r\n\r\nL- 	Law Enforcement:  Report it at  https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684f8 https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684f9  or call 1930. 	\r\n	\r\nB- 	Bank:  Inform HDFC Bank  immediately so we can help secure your account. 	\r\n	\r\nW- 	Wipe:  Reset your device and update all passwords. 	\r\n	\r\n	\r\nShare these safety tips with your parents and grandparents to help them stay protected from cyber fraud. \r\nYour safety is our top priority, and we are always here to help. \r\nPlease contact your nearest Branch or Relationship Manager if you have any questions or concerns. 	\r\n	\r\nSecurity is a mutual commitment. Stay vigilant. \r\n\r\n#CyberJagritBharat 	\r\n	\r\nWarm Regards, \r\nHDFC Bank \r\n	\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n*Terms and conditions apply |  https://t13.mailers.hdfcbank.net/r/?id=tece09cdf-129b-496c-abc8-86c505133dae,183238,684fa&e=cDE9JTQwU0lNZWV6YWh5WmtJcDE3ZFRyeDF2NnZMeWZ3TktRRmF6aVJlZ1FmWUdESTlYdkh2N3Vsamdmc29iMW40NnZZcVMxU2pSaGxNajVCQzNOekZ6Q3pGJTJGZ3h3UXhPb3dzTkwydiUyQmM2QjI0JTJCWjQlM0Q&s=p5HoG_OU5vm7uXgP6xv6LvkeeaFpHfVU4tgUt8n_ouY Unsubscribe 	\r\nSoni_7-10-25\r\n', '2025-12-17 10:43:57', 'unread', 0),
